<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF8A6A35F81C9A38140FB625" pageId="113" pageNumber="871" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF8A6A35F81C9A38140FB625" blockId="113.[2014,2608,3003,3430]" pageId="113" pageNumber="871">
Originally described in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF8A6A35F6C59A38179DB748" authorityName="E. Geoffroy" authorityYear="1818" box="[2361,2461,3169,3194]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Plecotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="113" pageNumber="871" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Plecotus</taxonomicName>
, but morphological, karyological, and molecular analyses indicated its distinctness from Old World 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF8A6A35F7BE9A9616A5B7C2" authorityName="E. Geoffroy" authorityYear="1818" box="[2114,2213,3279,3312]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Plecotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="113" pageNumber="871" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Plecotus</taxonomicName>
, supporting its inclusion in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF8A6A35F81E9AAF168BB625" authorityName="H. Allen" authorityYear="1865" box="[2018,2187,3318,3351]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Corynorhinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="113" pageNumber="871" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Corynorhinus</taxonomicName>
. Five subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
